dct_title_s: West Indies and Central America ; Florida
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures. Prime meridians: Greenwich and Washington, D.C. Insets: Map of the island of Cuba -- Map of the island of Jamaica -- Map of the Panama Railroad and proposed canal -- Map of the proposed Nicaragua canal route -- Map of the proposed ship rail road route accross [sic] the Isthmus of Tehuantepec -- Map of the Bermuda Islands. In upper margin: 71--72. Probably issued in: Mitchell's new general atlas ... Philadelphia : Wm. M. Bradley & Bro., 1884.
